long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Add support for Symantec WSS Roaming Captive Portal to Google Chrome.

Allows chrome browser to connect to Symantec Web Security service without experiencing CORS authentication errors.
